Basic Array problems in striver sheet(Easy level):
Given an array we have to return the Largest element in the array

Time Complexity :O(n)
Space Complexity : O(1)
********************
Java Implementation:

class Solution {
    public int largestElement(int[] nums) {
        int max=0;
        for(int i=0;i<nums.length;i++){
            max=Math.max(max,nums[i]);
        }
        return max;
    }
}
